# SaaS Flash Report - Project Brief

## Site Overview
SaaS Flash Report delivers real-time software-as-a-service intelligence to SaaS founders, enterprise buyers, and B2B technology professionals. Daily aggregation of product launches, pricing changes, enterprise deals, and cloud infrastructure developments.

**Domain**: saasflashreport.com  
**Theme**: Indigo (#6366F1)  
**Tagline**: "Software Success at Software Speed"  
**Emoji**: ⚙️  

## Target Audience
- **Primary**: SaaS founders, operators, and B2B software professionals
- **Secondary**: Enterprise software buyers, CTOs, and technology decision-makers
- **Tertiary**: Software developers, cloud infrastructure professionals, API developers

## Content Focus Areas
- **Product Launches**: New SaaS products, major feature releases, platform launches
- **Pricing Changes**: New pricing models, feature tiers, subscription updates
- **Enterprise Deals**: Large contracts, partnerships, integrations
- **Acquisitions**: SaaS company buyouts, strategic acquisitions
- **Platform Updates**: API changes, infrastructure improvements, security updates
- **API Integrations**: New partnerships, third-party integrations, marketplace additions

